  ('optician-moex-01964', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位老花眼者驗光後的度數為-2.00DS/-1.50DC×175, OU。在40 cm測試距離測出的正相對調節值（PRA） 為-0.25 D。若他習慣的工作距離（customary working distance）為25 cm，要達到舒適的調節力（comfortable accommodation），他大約還需要多少近距離附加度（near ADD）？', '["+4.00 D", "+3.25 D", "+2.75 D", "+1.25 D"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b5729e769b59", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e88e08bae45b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01965', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不屬於決定初步的近距離附加度（near ADD）方法之一？', '["正負相對調節（NRA/PRA）檢查", "調節靈巧性（accommodative facility）檢查", "融像性交叉圓柱鏡（FCC）檢查", "依年齡預測"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b5729e769b59", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e88e08bae45b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01966', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '測量調節幅度時，使用負鏡片模糊法（minus-lens-to-blur test）與推近法（push-up test）之間的差別，下 列何者正確？', '["近感知刺激調節（proximal stimulation to accommodation）在負鏡片模糊法是固定的，而在推近法會改變", "視標的改變在負鏡片模糊法為持續性（continuous），而在推近法為間斷性（discrete）", "在進行測驗時，視標的影像大小之變化在負鏡片模糊法是較大於推近法", "負鏡片模糊法的調節力終點（accommodative endpoint）會比推近法還要好"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b5729e769b59", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e88e08bae45b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
